# _redirects — Civil Engineering Suite (Cloudflare Pages)
# Static path rewrites: public/* files served at clean URLs
# 200 = silent rewrite (no URL change in browser)
# Must be placed BEFORE any catch-all rules.
#
# FIX 3A — Fonts: /fonts/* → /public/fonts/:splat
#   Physical location: public/fonts/*.woff2
#   Browser requests:  /fonts/*.woff2
#   Without this rewrite, all font requests 404.
#
# FIX 3B — Images: /footing-pro/images/* and /images/*
#   Physical location: public/footing-pro/images/* and public/images/*
#   Browser requests:  /footing-pro/images/* and /images/*
#   These rewrites must exist for images to load at all.
#
# FIX L1 — Landing pages: /footing-pro/{engineers,offices,students}/*
#   Physical location: public/footing-pro/{engineers,offices,students}/index.html
#   Browser requests:  /footing-pro/engineers/  /footing-pro/offices/  /footing-pro/students/
#   Root cause of 404: landing HTML files live inside public/ (same pattern as all
#   other static assets) but no rewrite rule existed to map the clean URL to the
#   physical path. Without this rule, Cloudflare Pages file serving never finds the
#   files — it only looks at the literal request path, not inside public/.
#   These rules MUST appear BEFORE /footing-pro/images/* to prevent order ambiguity.
#   The [[path]].js STATIC_PASSTHROUGH also updated to explicitly pass these paths
#   through without entering the ROUTES encrypted-app matching loop.

/footing-pro/engineers/*    /public/footing-pro/engineers/:splat    200
/footing-pro/offices/*      /public/footing-pro/offices/:splat      200
/footing-pro/students/*     /public/footing-pro/students/:splat     200

/fonts/*                    /public/fonts/:splat                    200
/images/*                   /public/images/:splat                   200
/footing-pro/images/*       /public/footing-pro/images/:splat       200
/beam-pro/images/*          /public/beam-pro/images/:splat          200
/column-pro/images/*        /public/column-pro/images/:splat        200
/deflection-pro/images/*    /public/deflection-pro/images/:splat    200
/earthquake-pro/images/*    /public/earthquake-pro/images/:splat    200
/mur-pro/images/*           /public/mur-pro/images/:splat           200
/add-reft-pro/images/*      /public/add-reft-pro/images/:splat      200
/section-property-pro/images/* /public/section-property-pro/images/:splat 200
